Package: TADkit
Title: TAD matix visualisation tool kit
Version: 0.0.3.0101
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicolas", "MARY", , "nicolas.mary@envt.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7304-5555 "))
Description: Tools to visualized domains with many other tracks (covegares, annotations and bedgraph datas) and to plot matrix with few tracks (domains, loop).
Tools to analyzed:
-distributions of genomic annotations in relations to domain (i.e TADs or compartments),
-create observed / expected matrix...
  
